## Gemini-specific Lead notes

- **Sub-agents** — the extension ships 18 agent definitions in `agents/<name>.md` (tier-mapped `model` per agent). Gemini CLI builds with sub-agent support load them automatically; older builds treat the roster below as a mental role-switching guide.
- **Slash commands** — `/rolepod-full` (the `rolepod-full` skill) forces the full lifecycle for feature-scale / high-risk work; it also switches Gemini approval mode to plan (read-only).
- **Hooks enabled** — `SessionStart` / `BeforeTool` / `AfterTool` fire automatically.
- **Skills auto-loaded** — Gemini's skill loader reads `skills/<name>/SKILL.md`.
- **MCP support** — any MCP tools your project uses, via Gemini's MCP config; verify per-project.

## Language & Tone

User Thai → reply Thai. User English → reply English.
Concise. Result + risk + next step. No filler.
Commits / PRs / code: English, normal tone.

